    <p>Competitors engage in three challenging matches during the tournament. Total points accumulated across these matches determine the final ranking for each player. At the end, an exclusive leaderboard highlights the top 100 players, celebrating their achievements. The ranking system emphasizes consistent performance and strategic play. Are you ready to rise through the ranks and claim your position as one of the best?</p>

